    {
      "id": "document-view-contract-required",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Required Data",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -970,
        "y": 385
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Required\n\nThe document view MUST render composed content.\n\nRequired fields in `data`:\n- `viewRole: \"document\"`\n- `viewKind: \"display\"`\n- `documentHtml` (string) OR `documentBlocks` (ordered array)\n\nOptional:\n- `partNodeIds` (ordered list of source nodes)\n- `documentOrder` (resolved order)\n- `title` and `titleSourceNodeId`\n\nIf `documentHtml` and `documentBlocks` are both missing, the view must fall back to an explicit error surface.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
