    {
      "id": "document-view-contract-render",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Render Rules",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -330,
        "y": 385
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Render Rules\n\n- Render the **document body** first.\n- Title is optional and may be derived from `titleSourceNodeId`.\n- Do not render port cards, icon glyphs, or summary cards.\n- Support scrolling inside the document surface.\n- If document content is missing, render an explicit error card.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
