    {
      "id": "document-view-contract-composition",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Composition",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": 310,
        "y": 385
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Composition\n\n- Document parts are ordered by `documentOrder` or the template's declared ordering.\n- Parts are rendered in a single vertical stack.\n- Part types include: markdown, section, reference, figure, embed, annotation, summary.\n- The document view must not reflow parts into cards or port surfaces.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
