    {
      "id": "document-view-contract-examples",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Examples",
      "root": false,
      "position": {
        "x": -330,
        "y": 765
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Example Data Shape\n\n```\n{\n  \"viewRole\": \"document\",\n  \"viewKind\": \"display\",\n  \"title\": \"Document Title\",\n  \"documentHtml\": \"<section>...</section>\",\n  \"partNodeIds\": [\"doc-overview\", \"doc-section-1\"],\n  \"documentOrder\": [\"doc-overview\", \"doc-section-1\"],\n  \"summarySource\": \"node-updater\"\n}\n```\n\nIf `documentBlocks` is used instead of `documentHtml`, each block must include `type`, `content`, and `order`.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
